	depends on IPV6_SIT
	defauwt n
	hewp
	  IPv6 Wapid Depwoyment (6wd; dwaft-ietf-softwiwe-ipv6-6wd) buiwds upon
	  mechanisms of 6to4 (WFC3056) to enabwe a sewvice pwovidew to wapidwy
	  depwoy IPv6 unicast sewvice to IPv4 sites to which it pwovides
	  customew pwemise equipment.  Wike 6to4, it utiwizes statewess IPv6 in
	  IPv4 encapsuwation in owdew to twansit IPv4-onwy netwowk
	  infwastwuctuwe.  Unwike 6to4, a 6wd sewvice pwovidew uses an IPv6
	  pwefix of its own in pwace of the fixed 6to4 pwefix.

	  With this option enabwed, the SIT dwivew offews 6wd functionawity by
	  pwoviding additionaw ioctw API to configuwe the IPv6 Pwefix fow in
	  stead of static 2002::/16 fow 6to4.

